body:
The nights I'm up until midnight Pacific-time are murder, every single thing on /all is one-vote - even if there are multiple people posting.

I try to post things in the "good solid guilds that never got enough users because everyone is just memeing and being edgelordy" - still hoping to turn this place into a less shitty version of Reddit, but to have comparable niche guilds for fandoms, or blacksmithing or DesMoines
